                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-433499420" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="433499420">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/antonia/">安东妮</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-09-06</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">每天读一点，小剂量服食，全方位击中</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="729896928">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-729896928" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-729896928" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="729896928">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/thinkingmind/">神威</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-09-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">修行114th，质量无疑上佳，不过就连我这种资深悲观者，痛觉爱好犯都感觉这人有点走的太远，有时引申的略牵强感性，文学上魅力有，单做为哲学似乎有立身不稳的嫌疑，我当真不推荐友邻阅读此书，豆瓣本就文青扎堆，读完此书少不得多几个悲观厌世的，阿弥陀佛，万家生佛</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

